ected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"connection_refused\",\n    \"deadline_exceeded\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shipping\",\n    \"checkoutservice->payment\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"cartservice->frontend\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"This component exhibited the highest latency spike while interacting with downstream services (ProductCatalogService, ShippingService, PaymentService, and EmailService). These delays are significantly higher than observed averages.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"For instance, `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` experienced a delay of 1369 seconds compared to a normal delay of ~14 seconds.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"ProductCatalogService exhibited downstream interaction with very high delays in serving 'GetProduct' and 'ListProducts' APIs.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Example: Observation where Frontend-0 was effected due unpredictably poor AVG-network roundtrip.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "通过对异常指标的分析，我们识别出了几处显著的异常调用链。以下是根据数据所提取的主要异常实体及可能的根因分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod 'redis-cart-0' experienced increased response time related to 'rrt_max' due to high resource demand possibly linked to Node 'aiops-k8s-08' resource strain.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"The 'rrt_max' for 'redis-cart-0' significantly increased with a median change ratio during the fault period, and 'pod_cpu_usage' also showed notable variations indicating resource contention.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Adservice exhibited service performance degradation